name: Meteorite
description:
It's a falling star of anger. Bomb people around you with emotions. It's tiring for us. Do you know? no one want to be like this. I hope I am only a star not falling star nor meteorite. I'm trying, I hope you can see.

I'm collecting my thought with this super short animation.I call it LongTake since it is a one time drawing and animating and done. I found stories in every single change, every line I added. It gave me more space to describe what in my mind.
